data.description: Move in Ready. Beautiful 4 bedroom home in a desirable community. Upgraded Kitchen with Granite counter tops, new sink and faucet, beautiful back splash, stainless steel appliances, a large amount of cabinets, and a breakfast bar. Many upgrades such as a large new dream style walk in shower, walk in closets, exterior of home recently painted, pool equipment and piping upgraded recently to the awesome conventional pool with pool cover, security fence and gate around back porch for pool security, extra canopy to extend the porch for additional comfort and shade, self contained 4 person spa, no  care artificial turf in back yard with cherry, plum and lemon trees, front security door and front yard irrigation, awesome   Mountain views.
